text: Rezső Velez (31 August 1887 - 15 May 1971) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics and seven events at the 1924 Summer Olympics.Rezső Velez's obituary ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:People from Komárom
